description: Welcome to your ideal city retreat—a stylish 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom penthouse duplex perched on top of this professionally managed building on South Boston’s desirable West Side. Just 0.3 miles from the Red Line & seconds from trendy restaurants, bars, fitness studios & coffee shops, this home puts everything you need within a quick reach. As soon as you open the door you will notice this sun-drenched home offers an open-concept main floor has a sleek kitchen with stainless steel appliances, newly finished hardwood floors throughout & tons of natural light. Upstairs, two spacious bedrooms and a flexible bonus area give you room to create a home office, guest space, or workout zone. Step out onto your private deck perfect for catching up with friends or winding down after a busy day. Plus, enjoy the rare bonus of two tandem garage parking spots. Whether you're commuting downtown, working remotely you will find an ease with this condo. Easy to show!
